## .gitignore for ScrumFlix ASP.NET Core MVC

# User Secrets (NEVER commit)
**/secrets.json
**/usersecrets/

# Build artifacts
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
*.user
*.suo
.vs/

# Publish output
publish/
*.pubxml
*.pubxml.user

# NuGet
*.nupkg
.nuget/
packages/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log
logs/

# Environment-specific config
appsettings.Production.json
/ScrumFlix/Views/Movies/MovieCatalog - Copy.cshtml
/ScrumFlix/wwwroot/css/scrumflix_old.css
